              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4857200-maven?shelf=made-into-a-movie">made-into-a-movie</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer153435008" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4750903792025520918">I struggled with this book a bit at first, especially with so many characters to keep track of. I eventually got into it a bit, but with mixed feelings. I was interested enough to finish the book, but I&apos;m not sure I enjoyed the whole experience. The many typos and poorly edited translations in this edition didn&apos;t help either. Just ok.</span>
  <span id="freeText4750903792025520918" style="display:none">I struggled with this book a bit at first, especially with so many characters to keep track of. I eventually got into it a bit, but with mixed feelings. I was interested enough to finish the book, but I'm not sure I enjoyed the whole experience. The many typos and poorly edited translations in this edition didn't help either. Just ok.</span>
