<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/978689.They_Thought_They_Were_Free"><img alt="They Thought They Were Free: The Germans 1933-45" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1328873882l/978689._SX98_.jpg" />
